node.text: It’s been one year since we debuted ‘Grey Area’. I remember getting the idea for this concept and everything quickly falling into place. It went from an idea to a build series with my dude @mikeyojeda to a lunch party to showcase our work in a matter of months. Thanks for the love on this project over the year it’s so cool to chat with you all about the bike and what we had to do to make a street legal motorcycle be able to shred a Supercross track. Thanks to @mikeyojeda @gasproductions_ @dustin_humphrey @willynillyknowsbest and @ridgebenben for the help

node.title: It’s been one year since we debuted ‘Grey Area’
